{{Quote|Sevari andris spice &mdash; preferred 10 times out of 12 in blind sample tests by the Imperial Board of Foodstuffs and Cosumables &hellip;|[[Commission for the Preservation of the New Order/Legends|COMPNOR]] advertisement|<ref name="The Free-Trader's Guide to Sevarcos">{{JournalCite|2|The Free-Trader's Guide to Sevarcos}}</ref>}}
The '''Imperial Board of Foodstuffs and Consumables''' was an organization of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] that monitored the usage, quality, and safety of various foods, medicines, and other such substances. In blind sample tests, Board judges chose [[Andris/Legends|andris]] as a superior food additive ten times out of twelve of the time.

